Bootstrap and initialize a new Soma network

Usage: soma genesis [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  ceremony  Coordinate multi-validator genesis for network launches
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --from-config <FROM_CONFIG>
          Start genesis with a given config file
      --write-config <WRITE_CONFIG>
          Build a genesis config, write it to the specified path, and exit
      --working-dir <WORKING_DIR>
          
  -f, --force
          Forces overwriting existing configuration
      --epoch-duration-ms <EPOCH_DURATION_MS>
          
      --with-faucet
          Creates an extra faucet configuration for soma persisted runs.
      --committee-size <COMMITTEE_SIZE>
          Set number of validators in the network
  -h, --help
          Print help
